metadata.description: The Milky Way rising over Merrick Butte (far right) and the West and East Mitten Buttes at the Navajo Nation's Monument Valley Park. This astrophotgraphy image was taken over a 4 minute time lapse looking towards the east with light from the moon beginning to appear at the horizon. This image was processed to bring out the color and features of the Milky Way. The purchaser will receive a PNG file with the "preview" watermark removed.
metadata.title: Milky Way Over Monument Valley 1
metadata.subtitle: The Milky Way rising over Merrick, West, and Easy Mitten Buttes
